reviewText:
Awesome information,  Love Dani she is sooooo genuine and all info is so helpful when we put it into action.
Thank you

I bought this a few months ago, after I went to her seminar in Ohio. This program is chucked full of information. The hardest part about using this program is the discipline to quit wasteful spending, especially if thats been a lifestyle for you. If you listen to the instructions and do what your told, this WILL be a huge benefit for you and you will save far beyond what you paid for it.
There is SO much information in here. Did not realize how much money I was just throwing away. Here is to being debt free more easily and quicker than I ever dreamed possible.

I love all of Dani Johnson's CD's and seminars.  After this, I hope to pay off $40K in debt in less than 2 years.  Before this, it would've taken me forever, and then I don't think I would've achieved complete freedom from debt.
